definitions.definition: Not sufficient ; of a type or kind that does not suffice , that does not satisfy requirements or needs.
examples: It is a necessary condition but an insufficient one.

definitions.definition: Not sufficient; lacking competent power or ability ; unqualified , unequal , unfit .
